<div class="wrapper">
	<div id="description">
		<p>Are you tired of dealing with blurred vision? Enter to win a free <a href="http://www.nationwidevision.com/lasik/" target="_blank">LASIK surgery</a> ($2,000 value) by simply telling <a href="http://www.nationwidevision.com/" target="_blank">us</a> in 50 words or less why you should win a LASIK surgery over all your fellow compatriots. For an extra bonus point, feel free to submit your best cat photo with your entry. That’s right, we want a photo of your fluffiest, furriest little cat friend. Who knows? Your photo may just make it on our Facebook page….</p>
	</div>
	<div id="form">
		<%= simple_form_for @user do |f| %>
		  <%= f.input :first, :placeholder => "First Name"%>
		  <%= f.input :last, :placeholder => "Last Name" %>
		  <%= f.input :email, :placeholder => "Email Address" %>
		  <%= f.input :zip_code, :placeholder => "Your Zipcode" %>
		  <%= f.input :comment, :placeholder => "Comment" %>
		  <%= f.button :submit, 'SEND!', :class => "button positive" %>
		<% end %>     
	</div>
</div>
